metadata.name: VLVT Origin
metadata.description:
33 NFTs. 27 available (6 reserved for the VLVT team). Each one is 1/1 animated pixel art).

Owning a VLVT Origins token grants you unprecedented access to upcoming VLVT drops, private entry to the VLVT Discord VIP Lounge (role), and exclusive collaborations that you won't find anywhere else.

But wait, there's more! As a VLVT Origins passholder, you'll also receive free mint and be on the allowlist for all future VLVT NFT collections, giving you an edge over the competition.

Don't miss your chance to join the elite few who own a VLVT Origins pass and stay ahead of the game!
